# Fast Boiler

A CLI tool to generate a FastAPI project with a modern, scalable Repo-Service-Controller architecture.

## Installation

```bash
pip install .
```

Usage
Initialize a New Project

```bash
fast-boiler init my_project_name
```
Generate a New Resource

Navigate into your new project and run:

```
cd my_project_name
fast-boiler generate product
```
